.IP
none, pause, poweroff, save, shutdown
(none).
.PP
\fB\-\-apimon\-isln\-timeout\fR  Sets the isolation timeout in ms (30s).
\fB\-\-apimon\-resp\-timeout\fR  Sets the response timeout in ms (30s).
